 you will want to: @{" Register Your Copy " LINK "money"}

 And for those folks that need things spelled out: @{" Liability & copyright " LINK "legal"}

 DiskInfoTools was made with SAS/C and a GUI developer GadToolsBox.
 For quick and easy GUI development, GadToolsBox is *great* ;).
 (E-mail Jaba for GadToolsBox info at jaba@desert.wlink.nl).
